reports_En: The thorax was symmetrical, the mediastinal heart shadow was centered, no enlarged lymph nodes were seen in the mediastinum, the texture of both lungs was enhanced, and no abnormal density shadow was seen in both lungs; the bronchi of the lobar segment were clear, no abnormal density shadow was seen in the bilateral thoracic cavities, and no abnormal enhancement shadow was seen in the lungs and mediastinum after enhancement. Metallic shadow and its artifact were seen next to the thoracic vertebral plate

findings: 胸廓对称，纵隔心影居中，纵隔内未见肿大淋巴结影，双肺纹理增强，双肺胸膜下见弧形网状影及磨玻璃影，其内见小的低密度影；叶段支气管通畅，双侧胸腔内未见异常密度影。
terminologies: 双肺胸膜下见弧形网状影及磨玻璃影，其内见小的低密度影
impression: 双肺炎性病变（符合病毒性肺炎）
reports_En: The thorax was symmetrical, the mediastinal heart shadow was centered, no enlarged lymph node shadow was seen in the mediastinum, the texture of both lungs was enhanced, curved reticular shadow and ground glass shadow were seen under the pleura of both lungs, and small hypointense shadow was seen within them; the bronchi of the lobe segment were clear, and no abnormal density shadow was seen in the bilateral thoracic cavity.
